1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,796
Out in front. Didn’t run.

2
00:00:08,946 --> 00:00:12,743
Got there first just for fun.

3
00:00:12,893 --> 00:00:16,689
Everyone tries to pass.

4
00:00:16,839 --> 00:00:20,635
I don’t move. Make it last.

5
00:00:20,785 --> 00:00:24,581
Slow walk. Set the pace.

6
00:00:24,731 --> 00:00:28,528
What’s the rush to the same place?

7
00:00:28,678 --> 00:00:32,474
If time’s real, let it prove.

8
00:00:32,624 --> 00:00:36,420
I don’t chase. I let it move.

9
00:00:36,570 --> 00:00:40,366
They go fast. Call it drive.

10
00:00:40,516 --> 00:00:44,313
I go slow. Still arrive.

11
00:00:44,463 --> 00:00:48,259
Eyes on me like I’m wrong.

12
00:00:48,409 --> 00:00:52,205
But I’ve been here this long.

13
00:00:52,355 --> 00:00:56,151
Slow walk. Set the pace.

14
00:00:56,301 --> 00:01:00,098
What’s the rush to the same place?

15
00:01:00,248 --> 00:01:04,044
If time’s real, let it prove.

16
00:01:04,194 --> 00:01:07,990
I don’t chase. I let it move.

17
00:01:08,140 --> 00:01:11,937
If I’m late, who decides?

18
00:01:12,087 --> 00:01:15,883
Clocks just talk. I don’t buy.

19
00:01:16,033 --> 00:01:19,829
If I stop, nothing breaks.

20
00:01:19,979 --> 00:01:23,775
World keeps up. That’s the play.

21
00:01:23,925 --> 00:01:27,722
Slow walk. Say it twice.

22
00:01:27,872 --> 00:01:31,668
I don’t speed to feel alive.

23
00:01:31,818 --> 00:01:35,614
If it comes, then it’s mine.

24
00:01:35,764 --> 00:01:39,560
If it doesn’t, still fine.

25
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:43,507
Slow walk. Front of line.

26
00:01:43,657 --> 00:01:47,453
No one knows what is time.
